{
  "id": "RAW_6b327165",
  "title": "百倍性能提升、RPO=0：小红书亿级 MySQL 内核关键改造实践",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMjYzNjkzNw==&mid=2247635028&idx=1&sn=6ca869d1bb8fdb75f36c9ffcda015189",
  "date": "2026-03-15 23:16:00",
  "author": "dbaplus社群",
  "siteName": "dbaplus社群",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"us-4110356\">\n     <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88516\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;word-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:justify;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n        <div data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: -10px 0px;padding: 0px 10px;max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 100%;word-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <div hm_fix=\"461:527\" style=\"padding:10px;margin:0px;word-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;border-width:2px;border-color:white;box-sizing:border-box !important;border-style:solid;\">\n          <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: #7f7f7f;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: red;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去一年，小红书MySQL内核完成了0-1的建设，完成了3个解决方案和若干项优化，提出一种基于Binlog Server的数据一致性解决方案，通过提升半同步复制性能加速日志传输，在故障时可无侵入现有数据库架构地实现自动补数据，保证数据一致性。基于 MySQL 内核实现的合并秒杀优化，相对排队秒杀方案，将秒杀写入能力再提升5倍，相对 MySQL 开源社区版本更有百倍的性能提升。在设计上保持了和排队秒杀一致的能力，该能力对业务完全透明：仅需升级 MySQL 内核，无需改动 SQL，即可获得5倍以上性能提升。针对加列速度慢的问题，实现了秒级加列，加列速度将天级别变更缩短到分钟甚至秒级别。并且在稳定性、DDL速度、可观测性等方面都做了优化，在内部实现了80%+的部署。</span></span></p>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文围绕 MySQL 内核遇到的核心挑战，梳理已采取的应对策略，并提出后续可执行的改进方案。</span></span></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n      <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n       <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一、功能概览</span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在较长时间内，小红书业务对数据库性能、稳定性都有一些需求，依靠管控和中间件等规避了部分问题，但随着业务与实例规模扩张，上层规避问题成本高，底层内核优化杠杆效应更强、价值更大。下面简单列举几个核心痛点：</span></span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">遇到热门商品秒杀/热点笔记圈粉/大V直播带货等场景仍难以支撑短期高脉冲流量，热点行更新速度慢</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">和资金相关的核心业务的RPO=0的诉求</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">业务新需求需加字段，大表耗时太久，拖长业务交付周期</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在流量突增场景下的稳定性需求</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此，2025年启动建设<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">小红书自研版本 MySQL 内核 —— RedSQL&nbsp;</span>，针对业务上述痛点进行内核优化，逐一形成统一的解决方案。经过一年的发展，目前已完成了从0-1的建设，形成了3个大的解决方案和若干稳定性、性能优化，内部完成了80%以上自研版本部署。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，数据库内核功能大盘如下所示：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"153\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100151060\" data-ratio=\"0.2641107561235357\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1878\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e1b9eb3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZQRNrlIIrWcpysTl9VxqIbQ4YFXXajMlFpOwytNMUgPiafzDvjCiaN9fE29ibNDNNohMQmEKXqpmqo60Iny0maT9wg1x4a80jZd8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n     <div style=\"margin:0.5em 0;\">\n      <div style=\"background-color:#138bde;padding:0px 0px 2px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n       <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #fefefe;border-top-color: #138bde;border-right-color: #138bde;border-left-color: #138bde;padding: 0.5em 1.5em;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"line-height:20px;\" data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Emoji Symbols Font&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">二、RedSQL特性</span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面将详细介绍下三个大的解决方案，分别是数据一致性、热点行更新和DDL优化，阐述自研内核 RedSQL 发展的阶段性成果与思考。</span></span></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\" style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;border: 0px none;z-index: 0;\">\n     <div style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;display: flex;\">\n      <div style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;\">\n       <p data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;color: #138bde;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">1、秒杀能力再提升，热点更新速度提升到1.5W+</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对秒杀场景，目前有三种解决方案。将上述方案的瓶颈点和解决思路整合如下图对比所示，直观反映了各方案的优化思路。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"667\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100151061\" data-ratio=\"1.1538461538461537\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"624\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=972a7c67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYaFbbdYqjB2yv5fOYqay52Q7ekW6UBg4EXTyUb5K5IoC8ibyVgcOIWketg2j957kwsuEcSbRHCiam5TvOYQ7ekFxvl43XSfNrfibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.161812297734628\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"618\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"672\" data-imgfileid=\"100151062\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dcb4fcf2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYYZxmBJLRCK5gBiaLHqgstgG1D47IUIZiaGuticSCLbiaEj2mEJ2UGGONPaqWB9UNTxJrRc358WgurLXgm4cgPEH8yubbWPOzqXBrY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"671\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100151063\" data-ratio=\"1.1612903225806452\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"620\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=12d167af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYYLWvVb3T2f4lyjUQwX5TX83e8xtCicDzJcoxJMB3z5udgIMdHYOtrQutfCw9LZ9pjg1gYxiboG041IsxAia1UFk4h7ic9ZV800oNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">合并秒杀将多个事务 SQL 合并到一个事务进行提交，修改了MySQL的事务模型，必然涉及到MySQL事务系统、锁系统、Binlog系统等模块的修改。合并秒杀方案提供了如下优势：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）生态组件无感知：</span>将改动内容收敛到MySQL内核，输出的 Binlog内容和格式没有变化，对于DTS/Canel等组件无感知，避免了联动组件升级</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）内核升级无感知：</span>不修改InnoDB格式，不影响版本兼容性和版本回退</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3）业务SQL无修改：</span>和排队秒杀版本SQL语法兼容，可以动态开关。业务/DBA可以随时将合并秒杀退化到排队秒杀，也可以随时开启。可以同时将合并秒杀，排队秒杀，无秒杀在一个数据库同时跑起来，减少业务迁移成本。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在合并秒杀设计上，通过解决四项关键技术提升了数据库的性能 。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">缓存可见性：</span>通过新增全局缓存解决了数据可见性问题，通过排队方案解决了多线程数据一致性问题。方案中需要对数据库执行器大幅修改、精细调整，既要满足数据库ACID特性，又要提升百倍性能。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2834158415841584\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1616\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"164\" data-imgfileid=\"100151064\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ae2b7d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYaVmicicj8scCXNiaZEulQgNIlMO9pl9Zu6D8rU97Bg68QOkAkqbehp834aLHhmAq7UlQ4bRfWbaZIPwJ5EVv7Wze3biaec6GfYb7Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">行锁极致优化：</span>将秒杀过程拆分为<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">更新和提交</span>两个阶段，通过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">对存储引擎锁系统的优化</span>，实现了秒杀线程并行执行。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3937074829931973\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2352\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"228\" data-imgfileid=\"100151065\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0580add0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYYHy3whwiaE06TSQzWxmX0MqGmkGUibeqPibWImib8yYnW0BWeuYvmVaLsDEgSCRN3L2DiaLXkxKOnQ1JCCQAHicecnDjwXWFGics5b18%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">日志并行提交 与 宕机恢复优化 ：</span>将多线程秒杀日志并行提交，进一步提升秒杀性能。调整宕机恢复流程，保证宕机恢复后的数据一致性以及主从数据的一致性。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7292817679558011\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"724\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"422\" data-imgfileid=\"100151066\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=542e2655&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZLw9zzt7xliaXvOgM529gcyY0fuUQByicN3VMxGbQ0UbC8ibnkkMiacvbv4eAzKAwrPiaRHFh6NYr7zkpEvhl462ft0vHJwVr8lmTY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4455611390284757\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1194\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"258\" data-imgfileid=\"100151067\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bee2c7e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYb00xI9iaTvRobswSVHYiclIFyjlJRuAI12Sn3hjOAuk767YxV7ic1Yn2CGMWzJg6W9PhmZ0dv8ibibyYFyAczica4icTGSFZD38XeUdY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">收益：</span>一方面，成功支撑直播电商超级单品的高并发秒杀场景；另一方面，有效保障社区热点笔记点赞、创作者关注飙升等业务需求。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.406875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1600\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"235\" data-imgfileid=\"100151068\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b9700182&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYbN4MfLib5qnlecLDPzwm1NEOf2UgNS4yia7trH4MmoPzsvzMRicL2vMKmUsV8jm6lw9H5ddY48zeyDFQd6uVzKzauQqe59detDDw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\" style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;border: 0px none;z-index: 0;\">\n     <div style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;display: flex;\">\n      <div style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;\">\n       <p data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;color: #138bde;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">2、数据一致性解决方案，核心场景RPO=0</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">依托全自研的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Binlog Server&nbsp;</span>与&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">ORC 高可用组件</span>，在技术上的收益：</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）高速复制方案：</span>针对业内缺乏可靠稳定的 Binlog 持久化组件这一痛点，自研的 Binlog Server 模块仅需 1C1G 极简资源，即可实现 300MB/s+ 的高速数据复制；</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）无人工干预的一致性保障方案：</span>在主备切换过程中，以数据一致性优先为原则设计自动补数机制，最终实现全流程自动化的一致性解决方案（RPO=60s -&gt; RPO=0s），无需人工介入。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3936052921719956\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1814\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"228\" data-imgfileid=\"100151069\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bc76dcef&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZQiafKVNVyr6Yevtibh4zXxY3XS1QObib7m6shzbTELHtficibdEGKOv6cszicBdQzRnqFYrj1MXQ4IpxicIJXS9G13A6nZ942v1zKRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3273113708820404\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1882\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"189\" data-imgfileid=\"100151070\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d87c25f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYYkMUYhZ2bt7zF53Dic6NviaJED35fFZgaGWJibiaShNPZulGkMprUSHwFhD0XleBEn03uHXT1iaBJZ5icicdXO3pEXXbPpGauxDtVpns%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在这个过程中，解决了如下问题：</span></span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">问题1：完整的MySQL 协议支持。</span>既提供了轻量化方案，仍保留了完整的MySQL协议支持。</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8399122807017544\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"912\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"485\" data-imgfileid=\"100151072\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ca527278&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYaHQlvgiaPWYKMSzLaibnzOo8vf4j235417IDODJ4RRIksqHic6LdkicUYdRZWmgwARtbSialvR3GYamCd3o8xvTrtNCph3htfcGWJ4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">问题2：</span>自研的SQL语法解析器。提供了自定义的SQL语法支持，保证了现有运维体系兼容性。</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为实现对 ORC 的便捷管理，同时确保对现有运维系统与高可用系统无侵入，要求 Binlog Server 支持 SQL 语法，以此降低周边系统的开发与适配成本。为此，我们为 Binlog Server 自研了专属语法解析器：输入的字符串会先经词法解析器提取 Token，再由语法解析器生成语法树，最终实现对SQL信息的精准提取。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4911111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"284\" data-imgfileid=\"100151073\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d492146&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYYz9NIeickjSbxvdtibCsiantYt7gSSTrLeYrEtkuFic6chTbuOib1wqOVLicQIPcnPicjHNIu9CQJk4NJurwzH0GozREGVpnHqrCasUc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">问题3：主从节点注册。</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Binlog Server 支持级联架构，既可作为 Slave 节点，从上游接收并持久化 Binlog。也可作为 Master 节点，向下游分发 Binlog。基于这一特性，Binlog Server 需具备双向注册能力，严格遵循 MySQL 节点注册规范，灵活模拟主库或从库身份完成注册流程。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9586056644880174\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"918\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"554\" data-imgfileid=\"100151074\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6bf639a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZIdR1ZDOfSxiassexnVYfCxI5F2vOuAXapela2pJuDjpYxibia7cfotiav2NzED2pLGEGgGOmgFleiaIoEdbfZbBRgK2Ujiajia9Ofdg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9055441478439425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"974\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"523\" data-imgfileid=\"100151075\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=108b2f15&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYbjulWbv5PswNJVp1D9AKBHfKfO1Um3SDENT4iaNdosIOSE34MZZUbIelUHnpX3US2oAZweNZGPvgrm6pWicVHpWhjpN4iaSUHR7c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">问题4：半同步支持。</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Master 节点生成由若干 Event 构成的 Binlog 文件，发送 Event 时会在其头部添加 Header 信息。Binlog Server 接收数据后，先解析 Header 并判断是否需发送 ACK；若需发送，则将 Master Log 位点信息反馈至主库。主库收到 ACK，确认数据已在下游持久化后，即可完成 InnoDB 事务提交。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3403298350824588\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1334\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"197\" data-imgfileid=\"100151076\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=901d431b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYbCUibVkd5115OUIQXU01lbT7YU4NW7zK4AWjVtKgS7BGOInumCw6ljIZRlGqsDwEkueZC4XW2MKLQ8bA0MmwQXSsU5s2C10I74%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">终态方案 ：</span>最终结合ORC和Binlog Server 构建了完整的数据不丢失解决方案</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4100211714890614\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2834\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"237\" data-imgfileid=\"100151077\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ed75b6fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZ8gzkiaFSGLoSibLAb3zPacTfzWmQ8Lz8eibyzvVIuCpZb0cyKLdBslicy56ibHciaBPx13aMytQ0GsYzUgr1kcTLS0abWDbLL9HoCE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">收益：</span>覆盖100% 核心集群，大幅降低了RPO时间，支持了核心场景RPO=0的目标。</span></span></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\" style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;border: 0px none;z-index: 0;\">\n     <div style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 10px 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;display: flex;\">\n      <div style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;\">\n       <p data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;\"><span style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;color: #138bde;\"><strong style=\"max-inline-size: 100%;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;outline: none 0px !important;cursor: text;\"><span leaf=\"\">3、秒级加列，周级别变更缩短至秒级</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">XHS核心集群数据库版本仍在5.7，DDL加列仍然依赖于gh-ost工具。业务迫切需要秒级加列功能，因此增加了秒级加列功能。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">现有方式加列为什么那么痛？</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">MySQL 用 gh-ost 新增字段 “痛”，核心是它靠全量数据搬迁实现无锁 DDL：先建临时表、拷贝历史数据、同步增量 binlog，最后换表名。大表操作耗时久，占满 IO/CPU，还易引发主从延迟。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">技术挑战在哪里？</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">秒级加列的核心挑战，是元数据与物理存储解耦：需原子化更新元数据且不改动原数据存储，设计多版本元数据实现读写无锁兼容。同时要攻克主从同步对齐、低版本及特殊表结构适配、宕机后元数据恢复等难题。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.569327731092437\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"952\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"329\" data-imgfileid=\"100151078\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53a74bc0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZXtQlsVbDXoWPrcs5NOnIlNZHYPnZ5Hwt3X97Gcz1ZI36lyCnDNjgibLJtIvmWnQ6aVkh3XdaOia08WJ2sQoywfGiauQxgibyOZdI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">社区DDL新增列的处理过程有两个修改：</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）元数据部分：</span>对于列定义和列信息进行修改</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）数据部分：</span>给每一行增加列的默认值，这个过程涉及到整个表的重建</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100151079\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=20b81df8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZJWsBqYibtAIvM0HKq00UialzPeUOCGf2a8Gzjgqr9jsdJdK9eWBYgdibSFMILPPJbqZiacm4ZkODuuxKXibqZiakTX45X7ejEubK4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">RedSQL对元数据进行了修改，增加了原始列的数量以及新增列默认值两个信息。那么当进行加列DDL操作以后，只需要修改数据字典的内容，这个过程非常迅速。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100151080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=920611a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYbqFts3ok6mVHFaXtWyWWV2DWazgSzIIV0Yadgx55Jto1RBOLiaXQ5lymhqSLdqrYyfWzJBm4pgwqf525Yz7PdTMiaChJt6YiaOTo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如上图所示，如果对数据行2在DDL之后读取内容。首先会读取列数量为3，将数据行2的数据全部读取出来，再根据新增列默认值拼接上列4，最终返回给用户。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果业务新插入一行数据，那么新的数据行如何和老的数据行共存并且区分呢。在这里会修改Header信息，增加Flag表示并记录改行自包含4列数据。那么新数据读取4列就不用拼接，老的数据读取4列需要拼接。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100151081\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a05efe1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYavJWOz6mkmR6d6bmjxRYn50xoEhAibF6oClBBh2nAdwGuFJUzWplCeAjDibYKtR9gJr8WJ66gobh4ZUnwiabHWDc38wI4QZLW2Ws%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">解决了数据读写问题，如果又新增了第5列数据，并且新插入了一行数据，最终的形态如下图所示。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2851851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100151081\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a05efe1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYavJWOz6mkmR6d6bmjxRYn50xoEhAibF6oClBBh2nAdwGuFJUzWplCeAjDibYKtR9gJr8WJ66gobh4ZUnwiabHWDc38wI4QZLW2Ws%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最终的形态如下图所示，数据内容配合数据字典形成了一个版本链。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100151082\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=088ba3d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZ4iaG1OPibPdLuIff7DIbhrCPLW5Ziak5Z4WcUvAHo8u0quOTYlronukTOdNj6YHRLnR0MLbgotDx8uEk7E5KHFvdcqGESrFRZGM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">收益：</span>业务加列速度将周级别变更缩短到分钟甚至秒级别。</span></span></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86152\">\n     <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;display:flex;\">\n      <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n       <p data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"color: #138bde;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">4、其他内核功能</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">简单介绍部分内核特性。</span></span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">CCL：模糊限流-&gt;精准限流</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">限流能力从时间阈值到具体SQL模版，实现精准限流，保障数据库稳定性。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"511\" data-imgfileid=\"100151083\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1e415384&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYaEviafmIFnE7gkFguUFQ4iap33jmwLZRMYg3icCuEFOonWLgDpqRHdf3jWpagefrduko4ibiaF6kguB4Mw3FFTAn3hwJ3FlagjpAzc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">SQL语法扩展</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持select from update和Returning语法。用来直接返回被影响的行的数据，而不需要再发一次 SELECT 查询，TPS 提升20%。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7712962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"446\" data-imgfileid=\"100151085\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40b662f6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYZC5I0Tz3CG9vDOCZPCIA97yXRllVa1RSibEBxUbibN0KzprAub4pabt8dekNODtzuviac5Mw02js4NJDKvWp3D8C4LkIeCwYUqvs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">BP并行加载</span></span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"line-height:1.75;\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">数据库内存（Buffer Pool）<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">加载速度从300MB/s提升至1GB/s，提升3.3倍</span>。不会出现实例重启后，预热不充分导致的慢查询和主从延迟告警。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"151\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100151086\" data-ratio=\"0.2611111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78c6c5c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FgiamgWvCHDYYEPRibNcn79oibAVS4ETgoPwBT9rz8icpMVBAPmcnylLS9FWSQTFuotZyiciahLahE7KHtpbuA8icmxhLpq0hhdIPIc0nMdfFSFEuPk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"86122\" data-color=\"#138bde\" data-custom=\"#138bde